{"tid":1252831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「我唔知/我唔理。」","createTime":"2019-06-23T08:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:28:19.000Z","uid":62032,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3b2ed9c28ade2ad7fa1b8e44986796c7f31c64","tid":1252831,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"某啲人:<br />\n「我唔知/我唔理。」<br />\n「搞咁多嘢做乜。」<br />\n「我重有幾多年命啊？2047我都唔知喺邊囉。」<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家聽都聽唔少<br />\n但其實有冇諗過調返轉頭<br />\n補充多少少可以有另一番解讀？<br />\n<br />\n我哋:<br />\n「我唔知/我唔理，總之維持原狀，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好搞乜嘢修例</span>。」<br />\n「搞咁多嘢做乜，<span style=\"color: red;\">越改越衰</span>。」<br />\n「我重有幾多年命啊？2047我都唔知喺邊囉。<br />\n   但最少而家畀我哋過多陣<span style=\"color: red;\">安寧日子</span>好冇？」<br />\n<br />\n記得69遊行嗰陣<br />\n聽到有對長者夫婦同同行遊行人士傾計<br />\n話:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「之後個世界係你哋嘅，<br />\n我哋最多咪得返10幾年命。<br />\n呢刻我哋重出倒嚟就要出聲，<br />\n如果再唔企出嚟發聲，<br />\n你哋之後嘅路就好難行。」</span><br />\n<br />\n頭一句<br />\n我聽過好多次<br />\n但我真係好希望<br />\n第二嗰句有一日係出自我屋企人把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 加油呀長輩圖大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}